%% state_02_review_session.mmd — ReviewSession Status
%% Ref: review_session model (status: pending/in_progress/completed/disputed)
%% Reviews are PARALLEL (manager + peers independently)
%% Timeout: deadline column, force-close overdue sessions

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending : Auto-created when\ntask enters DONE category

    pending --> in_progress : First review submitted\n(manager or peer)

    state "Review Collection" as review_fork {
        state parallel_reviews <<fork>>
            parallel_reviews --> manager_review : Manager rates skills
            parallel_reviews --> peer_reviews : Peers rate skills\n(min 2 required)
        state parallel_done <<join>>
            manager_review --> parallel_done
            peer_reviews --> parallel_done
    }

    in_progress --> completed : All reviews submitted\n(manager done + peers ≥ required)
    in_progress --> completed : Timeout exceeded\n(deadline < NOW)\n→ force-close with\navailable reviews

    completed --> disputed : Reviewee disputes\n(with reason)

    disputed --> completed : Admin resolves\n(re-evaluate / override / escalate)

    completed --> [*]

    note right of pending
        Created per TaskAssignment (not per task).
        deadline = NOW() + 14 days.
        required_peer_reviews default = 2.
        Notifications sent to manager + peers simultaneously.
    end note

    note left of completed
        On completion:
        • Reviewee can confirm or dispute
        • Score calculation triggered (manual)
        • Spider chart + Trust score updated
        • Anomaly detection (DetectAnomalyCommand)
    end note
